 "text": "<img src=\"/magica/resource/image_web/banner/announce/banner_0388_m.png\" class=\"newsTextBanner\"><br />\r\n『マギアレコード 魔法少女まどか☆マギカ外伝』をご利用いただき誠にありがとうございます。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6月12日17:00より「精神強化」対象魔法少女を追加いたします。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p class=\"newsHead\">「精神強化」対象の魔法少女</p>\r\n<div class='pickUpDetail CARD ENHANCE'>\r\n\t<div class='pickUpCard'>\r\n\t\t<div data-nativebgkey='frame_light_rank_5' data-src='resource/image_native/card/frame/frame_light_rank_5.png' class='pickUpCardFrame'></div>\r\n\t\t\t<img class='pickUpCardImage' data-nativeimgkey='card_40215_c' data-src='resource/image_native/card/image/card_40215_c.png' alt=''>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class='detailWrap'>\r\n\t\t<div class='attribute'><div class='attIcon type_f LIGHT'></div></div>\r\n\t\t<div class='charaName'>タルト</div>\r\n\t\t<div class='rarity MAX_5 DEFAULT_5'><span class='stars star1'></span><span class='stars star2'></span><span class='stars star3'></span><span class='stars star4'></span><span class='stars star5'></span></div>\r\n\t\t<div class='status1'>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>MAX HP</dt><dd>24260<span class='add'>(+7936)</span></dd></dl>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>MAX DEF</dt><dd>8998<span class='add'>(+3705)</span></dd></dl>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class='status2'>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>MAX ATK</dt><dd>8976<span class='add'>(+2004)</span></dd></dl>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>タイプ</dt><dd>バランス</dd></dl>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n<ul class='commandList'><!-- 所持ディスク:CHARGE,MPUP,RANGE_V,RANGE_H --><!--RANGE_V：縦　RANGE_H：横 -->\r\n\t\t\t<li class='MPUP'></li>\r\n\t\t\t<li class='RANGE_V'></li>\r\n\t\t\t<li class='RANGE_V'></li>\r\n\t\t\t<li class='RANGE_H'></li>\r\n\t\t\t<li class='CHARGE'></li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t<div class='connectWrap'>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>コネクト</dt><dd class='c_purple'>必ず守ってみせる！</dd></dl>\r\n\t\t\t<div class='description'>攻撃力UP[Ⅸ] ＆ 防御力UP[Ⅸ]</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class='magiaWrap'>\r\n\t\t\t<dl class='common_dl'><dt>マギア</dt